{"tid":1248234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"圍喺入面嘅警察要食晚飯啦 大家送啲食物畀佢哋食好冇","createTime":"2019-06-21T11:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T11:51:47.000Z","uid":24814,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"223daacb68cba3cf24c7286a8aeba69d99767e07","tid":1248234,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:42:14.000Z","msg":"香港的廢物挑戰嚴峻，當中根源問題之一關乎本地人均產生的廚餘量相當高，相比亞洲其他先進城市高出不少。在2011年，廚餘每天逾3,500噸，約佔棄置於堆填區的都市固體廢物40%。 有見及此，環境局宣布於2012年12月3日成立惜食香港督導委員會，聚焦於從源頭減少廚餘廢物。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2LcTd7v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2LcTd7v.png&h=2a6495d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U1BwLgx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU1BwLgx.png&h=9914c2e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mPQmn3d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmPQmn3d.png&h=aa23df0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好做大嘥鬼 我哋將食唔哂嘅嘢 例如雞鬼 蕃茄 同其他食物畀圍困嘅警察食 但係現場太多人 行唔到上前 <br />\n所以 我哋要用投擲嘅方法畀佢哋食<br />\n<br />\n雞蛋🥚要生 唔係咁多人鍾意食全熟蛋 生嘅可以畀佢哋可以決定點樣煮"},{"pid":"cb2d8726a12aa0bd33845a37df968ac0e00c8a03","tid":1248234,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:45:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"281c60ee176aeef272795ce5ff277b457258bd6a","tid":1248234,"uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EJEm7wB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEJEm7wB.jpg&h=51a333db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"290c8c2fee760ddef2c62a4c8d310a8aa2965cb8","tid":1248234,"uid":68220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:46:14.000Z","msg":"睇到都覺臭<br />\n天氣又咁熱"},{"pid":"c1635e6673f0f9d354635be31159e43a99e896cc","tid":1248234,"uid":61840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"281c60ee176aeef272795ce5ff277b457258bd6a","tid":1248234,"uid":2